      <h1>About Bird</h1>
      
      <section class="about-content">
        <h2>What is Bird?</h2>
        <p>Bird is an open-source microblogging platform that emphasizes simplicity and user privacy. Built with Ruby on Rails, it provides a space for sharing thoughts in 140 characters or less.</p>
        
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Post short messages up to 140 characters</li>
          <li>Reply to other users' posts</li>
          <li>Use hashtags to categorize posts</li>
          <li>Search through posts and replies</li>
          <li>Customizable user profiles</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Open Source</h2>
        <p>Bird is completely open source and free to use. The source code is available on GitHub, where you can contribute to its development or fork it for your own projects.</p>
